A '''Drace-2 Alert''' was a battle readiness alert to inform the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] of a military expedition or to prepare for a rescue mission. This was usually initiated when there was a need to rescue members of the expedition that were trapped either on a damaged ship or a ship that was in danger of exploding.

